data.description: Welcome to this wonderful residence, offering over 2800sqft of comfort! This inviting single-family home features a thoughtfully designed layout with split bedrooms, an open living area, and a spacious kitchen. On the main floor, discover one of two master bedrooms with its own master bath and a roomy walk-in closet—ideal for creating a welcoming mother-in-law suite. Another master suite, along with two additional guest rooms and a well-appointed guest bath, ensures privacy for your guests.  The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, adding convenience, and the entire house boasts timeless hardwood floors. Recent updates in 2023 include a new roof and a screened back patio, providing peace of mind and a serene outdoor space. Previous owners added thoughtful touches like an office space with built-in bookshelves, a cozy media room, and a charming lanai porch, creating spaces to enjoy the fresh air.  Upstairs, the second floor reveals another spacious master bedroom with walk-in closets and an exquisite master bath. Don't miss the opportunity to call this exceptional residence your own; schedule a viewing today! Experience the comfort and convenience that define this captivating and generously-sized home, complete with two master suites perfect for a mother-in-law setup. Seller will contribute up $7500 to buyer closing cost and prepaids and a $2000 bonus to buyer agent at closing.
